DirectJNgine is an Open Source library that provides a Java-based implementation of the Ext Direct API.

This software uses the ExtJs library (http://extjs.com), which is distributed under the GPL v3 license (see http://extjs.com/license).

For additional information about Ext Direct, read Introducing Ext Direct in the ExtJs website .
